---
// About Me component
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Tentang Saya</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Seorang developer yang passionate dalam menciptakan solusi digital yang inovatif dan user-friendly
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Profile Image -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="w-80 h-80 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-400 to-secondary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-72 h-72 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-64 h-64 bg-gray-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-gray-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Decorative elements -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-500 rounded-full opacity-60"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-6 h-6 bg-secondary-500 rounded-full opacity-60"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Halo, Saya Afif!</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Saya adalah seorang Full Stack Developer dengan pengalaman dalam mengembangkan aplikasi web modern menggunakan teknologi terdepan. 
              Saya memiliki passion yang besar dalam menciptakan solusi digital yang tidak hanya fungsional, tetapi juga memberikan pengalaman pengguna yang luar biasa.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Pendidikan & Pengalaman</h4>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  <span class="font-medium">Bachelor's Degree</span> - Teknik Informatika, Universitas Terkemuka
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  <span class="font-medium">3+ Tahun</span> pengalaman dalam pengembangan web dan mobile
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  <span class="font-medium">Freelancer</span> dengan berbagai proyek sukses untuk klien internasional
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Keahlian Utama</h4>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Frontend Development</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Backend Development</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Mobile Development</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">UI/UX Design</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Database Design</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Cloud Computing</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-4">
            <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">
              Hubungi Saya
              <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
